s/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50556d03ae7ed6b929beb31f31309c6d5b672ac9","tid":1687242,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:19:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac3db2590509e4f6ec5a113c52ee8040049df67e","tid":1687242,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5966f541c66c1958d01b17b77817465405add79","tid":1687242,"uid":147182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"你個App唔係太好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"成日都唔知果頭冇定hand左機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc5534f3bebb95e0dcf670f13a3f318662f6477","tid":1687242,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8be1d2b0e4c2f5333ce3cfe0f6e5d48c4aed72","tid":1687242,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a5ffcd84952d5bfde6af483319c37bf14d5a39","tid":1687242,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"係你哋講緊要擴發黃色經濟圈個時，一班手足已經貼緊<span style=\"color: red;\">Whatsgap</span><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">自家製黃店認證貼紙</span></strong>！係開Whatsgap個時都有海報彈出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Q: Whatsgap貼紙跟米豬連貼紙有什麼不同？</span><br />\nA: 有鑑於市面上已經存在許多由不同有心人所印整的米豬連貼紙，當中亦難免會有偽裝的情況出現。因此我們Whatsgap決定自家印製貼紙，上面有獨特的QRcode可以<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">避免有偽黃店自行印刷</span></strong>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\nQ:派發貼紙的準則是什麼？</span><br />\nA: 我們是根據由Whatsgap 提供的名單派發貼紙，而名單上的店舖是由網民報料，後經admin網上認證（FB專頁等）/有做實事而出現在名單中。當然，不排除仍有偽黃店出現，大家在app裏的報料區報告。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Q:什麼是黃色經濟圈？</span><br />\nA:為支持勇於表態的黃店，大家以優先選擇黃店為日常衣食住行等購買，發揮香港人互相幫助的精神。同時鼓勵更多商店表態，向政府證明香港人對抗極權的意志，將抗爭融入生活。同時謝絕一切中資企業、藍色店舖，向支持極權暴政的商業說不。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\nQ：黃色經濟圈會帶來什麼效果？</span><br />\nA：大家的資金會在黃色經濟圈裡面流動同增值。大家支持黃店令黃店老闆同員工都受惠，吸引更多志同道合的店舖成為黃店，亦吸引更多持相同立場的香港人來黃店消費。周而復始，各黃店的收入並不會隨着現今世道而下降，相反能得到更多同路人的支持而增加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後大家見到呢個貼紙就知係Whatsgap 內的黃店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要多多懲罰</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8NKJAkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8NKJAkb.jpg&h=c2ccf5f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZdBVkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZdBVkb.jpg&h=2944a495&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:37:16.000Z","msg":"我認為應該整雷射商標會易d 識別真偽"},{"pid":"e25d9c4e9f1a201b1335c0db65c118a57db44c4d","tid":1687242,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得咩貼紙咩認證貼埋間鋪係咪藍扮黃<br />\n都可以次一步先搞<br />\n<br />\n首要係推廣到去未有呢個黃色經濟圈concept既食客同老闆，如果佢地唔係上開網可能內心黃但鋪面又冇咩表態/ 唔知可以點做<br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得深黃老闆都可以做多d，例如鋪面呼籲人唔好食死一間，試下區內籌組成一個類似聯盟，再係鋪面互相介紹/ 憑單去另一間就減價優惠<br />\n咁樣先多黃店可以長久做落去<br />\n<br />\n我係琴日見呢張文宣諗到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftg7Yez.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fftg7Yez.jpg&h=6812597c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa628795dc37f237384559180fbb3643b832389b","tid":1687242,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6c679249f909cb0146974e99a17f996db9b898","tid":1687242,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"直接貼教學文<br />\n日程表 咪得 使乜咁麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:59:43.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n順手文宣"},{"pid":"97f060f503d0a7b4c582630f64504f88a42c1f21","tid":1687242,"uid":278570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB